  <data key="d2">28</data>
  <data key="d3">than my own death. But you have a husband and lovely
children; you may be happy. Heaven bless you and make you so! My unfortunate guest regards me with the tenderest compassion. He endeavours to
fill me with hope and talks as if life were a possession which he valued. He
